cat << EOF
With this package you can monitor running
processes based upon an XML configuration file,
XML string, INI file or an array where you
define patterns, conditions and actions.
XML::Parser must be installed to configure
System::ProcWatch by XML, additionally
Console::Getopt and XML::DTD must be installed
if you want to use the shipped shell scripts
'procwatch' and 'procwatch-lint'.
A simple 'ps' fake for WinNT can be found at
http://dev.iworks.at/PEAR/ps/ps.zip
EOF

